@node "INSTALL" " Installation "
Installation

There exist two Versions of BTDSnow 1.0. The first Version is for Kickstart
>=3.0 (>=V39) and planar-optimized.

Use this if:

- you don't have Kickstart 3.1 (V40)

- if you got no graphic-board

- if you use the EGS-Emulation


The other Version is ONLY for Kickstart 3.1 and up (>=40) and
chunkypixel-optimized.

Use this if:

- You have Kickstart 3.1, a graphic-board with CybergraphX or an other
  good emulation which emulates WriteChunkyPixels() (try it out).

So if you know which version you want to use, copy the file 'snow.btd' from
the directory 'V39' or 'V40' into your 'BTD:Blankers/' directory. That's all!
@endnode

